          <li><strong>Comparison search</strong> — "CPA vs bookkeeper", "TurboTax vs accountant for small business". Decided by trust signals.</li>
          <li><strong>Service-specific search</strong> — "construction accounting [city]", "restaurant bookkeeping [city]". Decided by niche service pages.</li>
